p Enhance your flight simulation experience with this square LCD monitor, designed specifically for playing games like DCS. With the ability to display the 2 or 3 MFD screens found in F/A-18 or F-16 jets as extended monitors, you can achieve a more immersive and realistic gaming experience. The monitor boasts a high-quality TFT full-color screen with a resolution of 600x600 DPI.

