p This monitor is fully compatible with Thrustmaster's MFD Cougar Pack, featuring two exact mount screw holes that allow for seamless integration into your existing setup. Additionally, the monitor's base features four additional screw holes for easy and secure mounting to your desk or stand, ensuring stability during gameplay.

p With its standard HDMI video interface, this monitor is easy to connect to any device. Most modern graphics cards support up to four monitor displays, making it an ideal addition to any gaming setup.

p In addition to its ability to display MFD screens, this monitor can display anything you drag into the window. For example, you can use it to display MSFS2020's instrument views, a music player, or even play a sports game in a small window while multitasking.

p Don't settle for a subpar flight simulation experience. Upgrade your setup with this high-quality square LCD monitor and take your gaming to new heights.

